snippet: The secretary for the Navy has requested that former Midshipmen quarterback Keenan Reynolds should be allowed to pursue his NFL career while fulfilling his military commitment in the Ready Reserves....
lead_paragraph: The secretary for the Navy has requested that former Midshipmen quarterback Keenan Reynolds should be allowed to pursue his NFL career while fulfilling his military commitment in the Ready Reserves.

headline.main: Former Navy QB Reynolds Gets OK to Play in NFL This Season
headline.print_headline: Former Navy QB Reynolds Gets OK to Play in NFL This Season
